    "body": "`TestCodeFormat` expects to find config file `\"tox.ini\"` in cython directory, see [runtests.py#L1585](https://github.com/cython/cython/blob/0.29.x/runtests.py#L1585).\r\n\r\nBecause `\"tox.ini\"` is not installed into site-packages, hence if one wants to test installed Cython, one must copy `\"tox.ini\"` into installation folder, or exclude style checks. \r\n\r\nIt makes sense to tie the location of `\"tox.ini\"` to the location of `runtests.py` instead.\r\n\r\nThis issue is meant to probe community's opinion on the proposed change. I will submit a PR if the proposed change is deemed appropriate.",
